OL,3,GHighlands & Eilean Siar
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry with variable
OL,6,Famounts of cloud and some bright or
OL,7,Fsunny intervals. There will be a
OL,8,Fscattering of showers across the west.
OL,9,FBrisk southwesterly winds in the far
OL,10,Fnorthwest.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FMainly dry this evening with
OL,13,Fsome late sunshine. Then the rest of
OL,14,Fthe night will be generally dry with
OL,15,Fclear periods and the odd shower in
OL,16,Fthe northwest.
OL,17,
OL,18,CSunday:FAll parts will have a dry day
OL,19,Fwith some sunny spells, some cloud
OL,20,Fbubbling up by afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
